{:spec/title "Control Plane Completion — Decision Wiring, Events, and Dashboard"
 :spec/description
 "Complete the multi-vendor agent control plane by wiring decision delivery
  to the existing approval system, emitting control plane events from the
  orchestrator loops, and building out the web dashboard views. The core
  infrastructure (state machine, registry, decision queue, heartbeat,
  adapters) is already merged via PR #326."

 :spec/intent
 {:type :feature
  :scope ["components/adapter-miniforge"
          "components/control-plane"
          "components/event-stream"
          "components/web-dashboard"]}

 :spec/constraints
 ["Build on the existing control plane components from feat/control-plane (PR #326)"
  "Decision delivery must use the existing es/approval system (event-stream.approval)"
  "Control plane events must use existing event-stream event types (:control-plane/*)"
  "Dashboard views are server-rendered Hiccup with htmx for live updates"
  "All tests must pass with bb test"
  "No changes to the adapter protocol interface — only implementations"]

 :spec/acceptance-criteria
 ["adapter-miniforge deliver-decision calls es/create-approval-request and bridges resolution"
  "Orchestrator emits :control-plane/agent-discovered, :control-plane/status-changed,
   :control-plane/decision-submitted, :control-plane/decision-resolved events"
  "Dashboard shows live agent grid with status badges, vendor icons, and task descriptions"
  "Dashboard decision queue supports both structured options and free-form resolution"
  "Dashboard summary bar shows agent counts by status"
  "All existing control plane tests continue to pass"
  "New integration tests cover decision delivery round-trip and event emission"]

 :workflow/type :standard-sdlc
 :workflow/version "2.0.0"

 :plan/tasks
 [{:task/id :wire-decision-delivery
   :task/description
   "Wire adapter-miniforge's deliver-decision to the approval system.
    In interface.clj MiniforgeAdapter deliver-decision, replace the stub with:
    1. Call (es/create-approval-request action-id required-signers quorum opts)
       using the decision's agent-id and resolution data
    2. Bridge the approval resolution back to the control plane by subscribing
       to approval-status events and calling the on-decision-resolved callback
    3. Remove the TODO comment at line 82
    Files: components/adapter-miniforge/src/ai/miniforge/adapter_miniforge/interface.clj
           components/event-stream/src/ai/miniforge/event_stream/approval.clj (reference only)"
   :task/type :implement
   :task/dependencies []}

  {:task/id :emit-orchestrator-events
   :task/description
   "Add event emission to the control plane orchestrator loops.
    In orchestrator.clj, add an event-stream dependency and emit events:
    1. run-discovery-pass: emit :control-plane/agent-discovered for each new agent found
    2. run-poll-pass: emit :control-plane/status-changed when an agent's status changes
    3. submit-decision-from-agent!: emit :control-plane/decision-submitted
    4. resolve-and-deliver!: emit :control-plane/decision-resolved
    The event-stream instance should be passed via the orchestrator config map.
    Use the event types already defined in event-stream/interface/events.clj.
    Files: components/control-plane/src/ai/miniforge/control_plane/orchestrator.clj
           components/event-stream/src/ai/miniforge/event_stream/interface/events.clj (reference)"
   :task/type :implement
   :task/dependencies []}

  {:task/id :dashboard-agent-detail
   :task/description
   "Build out the dashboard agent detail view and enhance the agent grid.
    In views/control_plane.clj, add:
    1. Agent detail panel (slide-out or modal) showing full agent info:
       vendor, status, task, last heartbeat, session metadata, heartbeat history
    2. Agent actions: pause, resume, terminate (htmx POST to existing API endpoints)
    3. Status filter toolbar for the agent grid (show/hide by status)
    4. Corresponding CSS in app.css for new components
    Files: components/web-dashboard/src/ai/miniforge/web_dashboard/views/control_plane.clj
           components/web-dashboard/resources/public/css/app.css"
   :task/type :implement
   :task/dependencies []}

  {:task/id :dashboard-decision-history
   :task/description
   "Add a decision history view to the dashboard.
    1. New endpoint GET /api/control-plane/decisions/history returning resolved decisions
    2. History panel below the active queue showing resolved decisions with:
       agent name, summary, resolution, resolved-by, timestamp
    3. Pagination via htmx (load more button)
    Files: components/web-dashboard/src/ai/miniforge/web_dashboard/server/control_plane.clj
           components/web-dashboard/src/ai/miniforge/web_dashboard/views/control_plane.clj"
   :task/type :implement
   :task/dependencies [:wire-decision-delivery]}

  {:task/id :integration-tests
   :task/description
   "Add integration tests for the new wiring:
    1. Decision delivery round-trip: submit decision → adapter delivers to approval
       system → approval resolved → control plane updated
    2. Event emission: verify orchestrator emits expected events during discovery,
       polling, decision submit, and decision resolve
    3. Dashboard endpoint tests: verify HTML fragments render correctly with
       test agent/decision data
    Files: components/control-plane/test/ai/miniforge/control_plane/orchestrator_test.clj
           components/adapter-miniforge/test/ai/miniforge/adapter_miniforge/interface_test.clj
           components/web-dashboard/test/ai/miniforge/web_dashboard/server/control_plane_test.clj"
   :task/type :test
   :task/dependencies [:wire-decision-delivery
                       :emit-orchestrator-events
                       :dashboard-agent-detail
                       :dashboard-decision-history]}]}
